              <ul class="terms-list">
                <li><strong>1. Acceptance of Terms:</strong> By accessing this site, you agree to abide by these terms.</li>
                <li><strong>2. Modifications:</strong> We may update these terms without prior notice.</li>
                <li><strong>3. Usage Restrictions:</strong> You are prohibited from using our site for unlawful activities.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
              <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Privacy & Security
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#termsAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ul class="terms-list">
                <li><strong>4. Data Protection:</strong> We take privacy seriously and protect your personal information.</li>
                <li><strong>5. Data Retention:</strong> We may retain your information for as long as necessary.</li>
                <li><strong>6. Security Measures:</strong> We implement standard security practices to protect your data.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
              <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i> Payments & Transactions
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#termsAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <ul class="terms-list">
                <li><strong>7. Billing:</strong> All payments are processed securely through our third-party payment gateway.</li>
                <li><strong>8. Refund Policy:</strong> Refunds are processed in compliance with our terms and conditions.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
   </section>
  

  <%- include("../partials/_footer.ejs") %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
